Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.74,0:00:02.73,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ここが学校菜園
Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.73,0:00:04.55,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃんがすごいの
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.55,0:00:06.96,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,花でも野菜でも　何でもできちゃうんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.96,0:00:08.32,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,グリーンサムなんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,さむ　誰　男
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.22,0:00:13.10,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,違う　植物を育てるのが上手い人のこと
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.10,0:00:13.84,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,さむが
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.84,0:00:14.99,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,違う　親指
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.99,0:00:15.60,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.60,0:00:18.27,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶わけわかんないことばっか言うよね
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.27,0:00:19.95,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　なんかいる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.83,0:00:21.90,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あ　それ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.90,0:00:24.42,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃん　この花なんていうの
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.37,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,お　あ　銀梅花って言ってね
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.37,0:00:29.61,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ハーブとかお酒にもなったりするんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.61,0:00:31.61,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あと　実がなって食べられるみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.61,0:00:32.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,へえ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.17,0:00:32.79,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,食べたい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.79,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,なんか星みたい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.53,0:00:38.97,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,魚いる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.44,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あ　晶駄目駄目やばいって
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.44,0:00:42.07,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.07,0:00:44.33,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,川に映った人影と目が合ったら
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.33,0:00:45.95,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,三日以内に死んじゃうんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.95,0:00:46.60,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.60,0:00:48.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,さっき目が合わなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.18,0:00:50.63,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あった　かも
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.34,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,し　死んじゃう
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.34,0:00:54.58,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,死んじゃうのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.58,0:00:57.31,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃん　大げさに言っちゃ駄目
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.31,0:01:00.41,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,足から落ちないようにっていうことだと思うよ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.38,0:01:03.58,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,やばいよ　葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.91,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,だからやばい落ちるって
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.63,0:01:10.21,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,目が合うほど川見てたらやばいよね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.38,0:01:14.67,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.43,0:01:18.24,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野柔術免許かいてになって
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.24,0:01:19.90,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,アリクイと戦いたい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.90,0:01:21.44,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,めっちゃ賢くなりたい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.69,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんかめっちゃ茸が食べられるようになりたい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.69,0:01:26.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小人を絶対見つけたい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.30,0:01:27.85,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,すごいね静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.85,0:01:28.88,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　そう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.77,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えへへ　褒められた
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.88,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ねえ　静留ちゃんって何で
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.25,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　なんでって
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.25,0:01:36.07,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,なんでそんなすごいの
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.07,0:01:37.25,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんですごい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.25,0:01:37.86,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.86,0:01:40.25,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そっか　なんでかな
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.25,0:01:45.15,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,やりたいからやりたいし　いきたいからいきたい　からかな
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.58,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,すごいなあ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.95,0:01:48.95,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,私は　何も
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.95,0:01:50.22,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,じゃあ応援して
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.22,0:01:50.83,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,あ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.83,0:01:52.57,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,お　えん　応援する
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.57,0:01:54.54,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,応援ならできる　かも
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.54,0:01:55.66,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私も
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.66,0:01:56.92,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私も応援する
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.92,0:01:58.67,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香のこと　応援する
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.67,0:02:00.04,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,無茶苦茶応援する
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.04,0:02:00.67,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,私
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.67,0:02:01.33,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.71,0:02:07.28,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あの　ピカーって輝く約束の星に約束する
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.66,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,約束の星
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.36,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,今つけた名前
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.91,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,シリウスじゃなかったかな　名前
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.04,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,じゃあ　それを私たちの名前にしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.04,0:02:16.86,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,いいよ
Comment: 1,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.87,JP-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.87,0:03:59.23,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,東吾野出てからどんぐらいかな
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.85,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,2、3時間
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.85,0:04:03.40,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,遠いよね　駅から駅まで
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.52,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,7G事件の前はもっと近かったのにね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.49,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんでもっと乗らなかったかな　電車
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.49,0:04:11.79,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,当たり前だったもんね　電車
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.79,0:04:15.51,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あん時乗ってれば池袋なんてすぐだったんだろうな
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.74,0:04:19.21,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吾野から池袋駅までちょうど30駅
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.21,0:04:21.23,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ってことはあと29駅
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.66,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,めっちゃ遠い　長旅だ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.35,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,元気かなあ　葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.90,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,元気に決まってるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.91,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,びっくりするかな
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.91,0:04:28.47,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.47,0:04:31.24,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,すっごい喜んでくれるよ　みんなで行ったら
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.23,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋まで時間かかりすぎて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.23,0:04:36.29,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私らおばあちゃんになってたらやだなあって
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ならないか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.70,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,その代わりに動物だ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.21,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,動物か
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.27,0:04:46.56,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,松茸さんたちさ　茸生えると寿命が短くなっちゃうって言ってたよね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.56,0:04:49.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,早い人だと1年で死んじゃうみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.73,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そう言ってたね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.85,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,でも生きてる時はすっごく幸せなんでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.93,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.43,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶はどう思う
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.43,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え　どうで
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.77,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,例えばだけどさ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.01,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,すっごく楽しく本さえ読めれば
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.39,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,他よりちょっと早めに死んじゃったりしてもいい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.56,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,もうその話よくない別に
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.58,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だってあの人たちもうすぐさ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.47,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.08,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶ちゃんすごく怖い思いしたから
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.08,0:05:15.95,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そんな怖い思いしたのに　私ら助けてくれたんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.55,0:05:17.66,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.55,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だよね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.62,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ごめん晶
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.33,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.44,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,てかさ　さっきからずっと何してんのポチさんと
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.32,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ポチさんめっちゃお尻かいてんじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.44,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,パンツ替えてないの
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.44,0:05:28.80,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.36,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ちょっと玲実ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.24,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.91,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,おパンツお履き替え遊ばせん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.91,0:05:34.77,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そうじゃなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.56,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,さっき洗濯したでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.16,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,着替えたの見たでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.85,0:05:39.84,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,見てない
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.84,0:05:41.36,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶隠れて着替えてたし
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.72,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でもその後一緒に干したじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.72,0:05:44.65,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あ　干した
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.58,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,馬鹿玲実
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.66,0:05:54.04,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,武蔵横手駅だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,えっと
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.96,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,なんともなさそうだし
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.06,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,何もなさそうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.78,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,とりあえずジメジメしてなければいいんじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,見て見て　ヤギヤギ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.04,0:06:14.59,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そういえば武蔵横手の駅前って有名なのいたね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.59,0:06:15.52,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そのヤギ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.66,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,違う気がする
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.70,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　だった
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.84,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,武蔵横手のヤギって二本足
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.84,0:06:20.98,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,へえ　そうなんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.61,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,違うの　聞いたの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.62,0:06:24.59,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,どういうこと
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.24,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　なんかこっち来てない
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.78,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,来てる来てる来てるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.11,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何なのあれ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.28,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,バフォーメットみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.43,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ヘルメットなのあれ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.24,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,じゃ話せるじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.29,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,おい　ぶつかってこないで
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.35,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なになになになに　あのヘルメット
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.35,0:06:53.18,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,バフォーメットは14世紀　フィリップ4世によって
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.64,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,テンプラー騎士団がターゲットされだどよう…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.24,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ポチさん
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.35,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怖くないよ　怖くない
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.05,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん 急いで急いで
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.47,0:06:59.94,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,8,,{\an8}やってるってば
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.77,0:07:16.10,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,何だったんだろうヤギさんたち
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.10,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,何がしたかったんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.44,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,わかんない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.16,0:07:24.07,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あんなのが　もしかしてあと28駅分
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.11,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,やめて　言わないで
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.44,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,交替するって運転は
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.09,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.09,0:07:37.18,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんに任せっきりは駄目
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.18,0:07:37.97,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.02,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確かにしずるちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.95,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野出てからずっと運転しっぱなしだもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.95,0:07:43.37,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,いいっていいって
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.82,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋行く言い出しっぺ私だし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.75,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,それは今関係ないでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.75,0:07:48.98,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ないことないって
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.98,0:07:49.96,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あるって
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.19,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あるよあるある
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.50,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ねえ晶はどう思う
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.21,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.73,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,みんなで運転交替した方がいいよね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.70,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あ　そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.70,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だよね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.81,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だってさ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.87,0:08:02.65,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.19,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.50,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんでそう思う
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.50,0:08:08.89,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,それは　単純に疲れて居眠り運転しちゃったら危ないし
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.01,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,交替交代で運転すれば
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.83,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,電車が動いてる時間が増えて
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.04,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,効率いいじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.12,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,池袋にも早く着くし
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.12,0:08:16.91,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そうそう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.72,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私も晶と同じに思ってた
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.75,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ねえ　いいことしかない
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.00,0:08:22.68,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.17,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんもちゃんと休んでね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.17,0:08:28.03,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋までどんぐらいかかるか分かんないからね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.58,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲実が学んだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.43,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,3日で池袋とか行ってたのに
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.49,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,すごいでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.45,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でも玲実に運転できるかな
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.49,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,できます
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.59,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,電車でGOだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.65,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それてきなやつやったことあるし
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.98,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,じゃあ食べ終わって　洗濯物たたんだら
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.98,0:08:42.48,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんの講習会
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.23,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,わかた
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.82,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,じゃあさっさと食べちゃお
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.68,0:08:48.65,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,昔は嫌いだったんだけどなゴーヤ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.10,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,最近なんか美味しい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.10,0:08:50.79,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,大人なった
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.96,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,こういう状況だから　特に美味しく感じるね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.96,0:08:58.73,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　猫兄たちが吾野さんゴーヤを高く買い取ってくれる理由が分かったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.34,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦いけど甘みもあるし
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.02,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あと旨味っていうの
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.25,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ああ　分かる分かる
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.40,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,旨味　旨味
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.40,0:09:08.45,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,逆に1日1回はゴーヤ食べないと調子出ない感じする
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.74,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,超分かる
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.62,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うん　どうした
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.62,0:09:12.45,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,トイレ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.95,0:09:13.86,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,行く
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.06,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,大丈夫　一人で
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.33,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　行っトイレ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.98,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,後は見た目だけ可愛くなれば完璧なんだけどな
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.61,0:09:29.08,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,茸が生えると　早い人だと1年で死んじゃうみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.08,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え違う違う平気平気
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.08,0:09:33.39,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,絶対平気だし
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.88,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,茸じゃなくて　おできだし
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.88,0:09:38.22,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,私おできできやすい体質だし
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.85,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ドーント・ワリー・ノー・プロブレム
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.59,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,龍彦にかけた平気
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.75,0:10:21.64,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,逃げよ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.64,0:10:22.57,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃん加速つ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.57,0:10:23.52,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ああ　はい
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.87,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶　こっちおいでこっち
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.87,0:10:45.07,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちゃんと洗わないと　またポチさんに嗅がれちゃうよ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.16,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,うっさい　馬鹿
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.32,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,零点玲実
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.65,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,平穏　静謐
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.99,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ずっとここにいたいな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.56,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん　止まる止まれない
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.48,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,とりあえず　止まらないで
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.68,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ゆっくりこのまま行く
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.93,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん　ゴルフのボールはいっばい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.93,0:11:41.12,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ほんとだ　いっぱい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.12,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やばっ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.12,0:11:42.91,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.65,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やばいやばいやばいやば
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.33,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,8,,{\an8}玲実ちゃん　怖いから
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.31,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,早く言って
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.98,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やばい想像しちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.83,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,武蔵横手駅のヤギ人間とか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.84,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,高麗駅の根っこみたいなやつとか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.31,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ここにあるボールってさ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.30,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,全部　元駅の周りに住んでた
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.00,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.01,0:12:12.08,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,人がボールで　さささ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.14,0:12:13.01,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,8,,{\an8}いや
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.76,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ああ もう やだやだやだやだ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.55,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんで怖い駅馬鹿なの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.25,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん　早くやっちゃって
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.00,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,さっき言ってた　えーと　何だっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.07,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ランチ・パック
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.56,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,スウィチバックね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.97,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ここから先はずっと向こうが先頭だから
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.71,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,奥の荷物を入れ替えよう
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.71,0:12:31.45,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.36,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,もう　怖い駅ばっかじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,どんどんどんどん　ひどくなってくよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.22,0:12:36.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,もう　吾野みたいに
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.22,0:12:38.81,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,人でなくても話ができるだけでいい
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.18,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,そんなことないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.60,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,また馬鹿にしようとしてるでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.12,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,話ができるってことはさ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.12,0:12:48.93,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嘘もつけちゃうし　嫌なことも言えちゃうし
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.94,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,喧嘩とかしちゃうしさ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.53,0:12:54.89,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,争いの種が一つなくなるんならさ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.89,0:12:57.62,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,喋れなくてもいい気がするな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.62,0:13:00.44,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,そんで　じーっとしてるの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.35,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,暗くて静かで　地面
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.06,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ええ 何何
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.10,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,何そんな
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.56,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんでお尻隠すの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.56,0:13:08.79,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,隠してない
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.63,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.80,0:13:12.56,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,見せて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.11,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,やだ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.11,0:13:13.84,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,見せろ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.84,0:13:14.91,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,絶対やだ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.10,0:13:16.93,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,きち
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.93,0:13:18.40,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何だ諦めた
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.59,0:13:18.61,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,8,,{\an8}やめろ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.61,0:13:19.58,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やめない
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.14,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ちゃんと見せて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.49,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶ちゃん　これって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.71,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,違う違う違う
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.71,0:13:30.48,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,いつから
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.24,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,平気
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.78,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,私なんともないから
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.74,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,どうかした
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.29,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶ちゃんに茸生え出た
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.29,0:13:35.87,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.86,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,こっちは大丈夫だから　そっちお願い
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.56,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,やだ　取らないで
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.84,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,せっかく安寧を手に入れたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.41,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,馬鹿
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.49,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,このままじゃ1、2年で死んじゃうの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.07,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,いいんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.73,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ペシミスティックでここいいし
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.85,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,私はこんなよくわからない世界で
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.85,0:13:51.10,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不安に苛まれながら生きていたくない
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.21,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶　昔っからそうなんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.21,0:13:55.72,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ひねくれてて一言多くてすぐ人馬鹿にして
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.39,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,やべい
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.18,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,零点玲実霊長類
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.29,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,自分になんかあっても　誰にも言えないで
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.60,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,大変なことになっちゃっても　無理して強がって
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.06,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,8,,{\an8}茸　茸　茸
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.51,0:14:07.40,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,本当は超ビビリで　超泣き虫だくせんねん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.59,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何　一体
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.13,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.17,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ね　晶
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.28,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶ちゃん　大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.42,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.28,0:14:31.03,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃん　静留ちゃんに　撫子ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.75,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,みんな変なの
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.35,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,晶はいつだって元気だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.95,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,元気もりもり
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.30,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.39,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.39,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,なんか変　だね
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.91,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,何言ってるの　撫子ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.52,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,晶変くないもん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.40,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ぷんすかぷん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.48,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何で
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.73,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あたしらの時は元に戻ったじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.73,0:14:52.07,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,こら玲実ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.10,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,そんな大きい声出したら
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.10,0:14:54.61,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,無依
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.97,0:14:58.53,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,もしかして茸が成長しすぎてたのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.53,0:14:59.98,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,すごい長かったし
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.98,0:15:00.50,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.32,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんか駄目なのも一緒に引っこ抜いちゃったってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.63,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,とりあえず座らせよう
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.58,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ほら晶
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.09,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,はえい
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.42,0:15:10.54,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,よいしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.93,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,おらあ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.97,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あらら
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.19,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,なんか思うように動けない
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.39,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,うん　何でかな
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.28,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,これって　あたしのせい
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.55,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,気持ちいいでしょね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.58,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,8,,{\an8}可愛いでしょね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.07,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,魂が　魂抜いちゃったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.89,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶の小憎らしい　サブカル魂
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.16,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　駄目だ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.73,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,病院みたいなのはない
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.73,0:15:37.05,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,やっぱスワン仙人の地図っていうか落書き使えない
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.12,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野戻ろう
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.74,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,今なら水引いてるかも
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.74,0:15:41.58,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,帰っても誰も直せないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.30,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,それにレールも曲がってるし
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.61,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ねえ このまま晶死んじゃったりしたらどうしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.35,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やだ　そんなの絶対
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.25,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,落ち着いて　大丈夫だから
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.25,0:15:50.93,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.90,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,必ず直せるよ玲実ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.47,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.92,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だって　私が
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.11,0:16:00.92,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,今日からあなたの名前はアンソニーでしょからね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.35,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,お願い善治郎さん　何か教えて
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.35,0:16:09.65,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,これから何があっても　くそじじいとか悪口言わないから
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.76,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,何だって
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.76,0:16:13.45,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,そいつは脳に直接影響を及ぼしてるぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.30,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,任しとけ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.74,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,今　反応にいんなら
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.56,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,口は悪いが　いいドクターがいる
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.57,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,以前一緒に働いていた
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.57,0:16:27.27,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小学校の頃　うんこを漏らして　俺のせいにした
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.27,0:16:33.10,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,カンニング事件　リコーダー　涎まみれ事件　全部俺のせいにした
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.34,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,今　稲荷山公園　ぼぼぼ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.77,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,くそ爺
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.41,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稲荷山
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.59,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稲荷山公園かな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.11,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　そうだと思う
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.11,0:16:47.73,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あカレー味のうんこ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.58,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,うんこの話はおしまい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.35,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,違う違う
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.35,0:16:51.72,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶が言ったのあの時
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.45,0:16:56.00,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,稲荷山公園には　いいお医者さんがいるって和代さんが
