Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:24.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,撫子姐 這朵花叫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,噢 啊 她叫香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:29.61,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,可以入藥 也可以用來泡酒
