Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:45.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,三日之內必死無疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:46.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
