Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:50.63,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,合了 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我 我會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:54.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,到底會不會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:57.31,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實 不要危言聳聽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:01:00.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只要腳踏實地不落入水裡就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:03.58,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這不行 葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,都說了掉下去不好的
