Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.25,0:01:36.07,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:37.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:37.86,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:40.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這樣啊 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:45.15,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,想做就做 想成就成 這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.58,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,你好厲害
