Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:00.67,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:01.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:07.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個 向著那顆亮晶晶的承諾之星約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.66,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,承諾之星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剛剛給它取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.91,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,它的名字應該是叫「天狼星」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那麼 就把它作為我們的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:16.86,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,好呀
Comment: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.87,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:59.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,從東吾野離開已經過去多久了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.85,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,二三小時嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:03.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好遠啊 車站與車站之間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,在7G事件之前明明很近的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼不多坐幾次列車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:11.79,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這是當然的啦 坐列車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:15.51,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個時候搭乘很快就到池袋了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:19.21,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,從吾野到池袋總共三十個站
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:21.23,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也就是說剩下其它二十九站
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,路漫漫其修遠兮 上下而求索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香她 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.90,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,肯定健健康康的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,會不會嚇她一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:28.47,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:31.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,肯定會非常開心的 大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,去池袋的時間太久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:36.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是我們都變成老太婆可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,應該不會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,取而代之的是變成動物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.21,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,動物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:46.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,松茸小姐她們說過 要是長了蘑菇壽命會非常短的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:49.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快的話一年之內就會死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.73,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,確實這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是活著的時候非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.43,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,只是打個比方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是能夠開開心心地看書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,比其他人早一點死也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.56,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,夠了不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,畢竟那些人馬上就
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.47,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.08,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶她肯定是非常害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:15.95,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且如此擔驚受怕 卻還救了我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:17.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,抱歉小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.33,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,說起來 剛才開始波奇它一直在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,波奇一直都盯著你的屁屁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你沒換內褲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:28.80,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.36,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實你注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要不要幫你換條底褲玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:34.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.56,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,剛才已經洗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是看到我換衣服了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:39.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:41.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你躲著換衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.72,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是這之後不是一起烘乾了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:44.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 烘乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,笨蛋玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:54.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,武藏橫手站到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.96,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感覺什麼也沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.06,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有碰見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.78,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,總之不要像回南天那樣濕濕的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快看快看 山羊山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:14.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說起來武藏橫手就是因為車站前而出名的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:15.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這隻山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.66,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感覺很不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔 站起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.84,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,武藏橫手的山羊兩腳站立嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:20.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 竟然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.61,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是啊 它聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:24.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不對 總感覺它跑過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.78,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,來了來了來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.28,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就好像巴風特·羊角惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感覺像是帶了個頭盔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,說不定也能說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂 不要撞到咱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什麼什麼什麼 這個垃圾頭盔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:53.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,羊角惡魔是十四世紀 法蘭西腓力四世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,鎮壓聖殿騎士團並使用酷刑逼供…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.35,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不要害怕 不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,靜留快點快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:06:59.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}我在快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:16.10,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那群山羊到底是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.10,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,到底想做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:24.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這樣的 難不成還要再過28個站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不要啊 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,輪班駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:37.18,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不能都交給靜留你做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:37.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,從吾野出來後一直都在開火車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:43.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去池袋也是我先說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.75,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這和現在並沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:48.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但沒必要就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:49.96,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明明就有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有的有必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吶 小晶你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.21,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,大家輪班駕駛會不會更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,畢竟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:02.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼你會這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:08.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這個 因為疲勞而睏倦 對駕駛來說有很大危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.01,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,如果是輪班駕駛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.83,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,列車行駛的時間也會延長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.04,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,會更加有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,也能更早到達池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:16.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是呀是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我和小晶想的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.75,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吶 好處挺多的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:22.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留要好好休息呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:28.03,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,畢竟我們不知道到池袋需要多久呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實學到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.43,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,明明三天就能到達池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是玲實你會不會開列車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,肯定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,雖然就玩過「電車啟動」這款遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這種事情我以前也做過的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.98,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那麼吃完飯 疊好衣服以後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:42.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留就開個講習會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那麼就快點吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:48.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,以前可是挺討厭苦瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,最近總感覺挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:50.79,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,長大成人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.96,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,在這種情況下 它的口味感覺特別好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:58.73,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 貓兄他們高價購買吾野苦瓜的理由我算是明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然很苦但苦盡甘來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這就所謂的「鮮味」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.25,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 我懂我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,鮮美鮮美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:08.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,反過來要是一天不吃一次苦瓜就會渾身難受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱超懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:12.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:13.86,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要我陪你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,沒事 我一個就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 去上廁所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,之後就是要讓它看起來更加可愛 就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:29.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是長了蘑菇 人最快會在一年之內死去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸不不不沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:33.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,絕對沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這不是蘑菇 是痔瘡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:38.22,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我可是有痔青年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不用擔心 問題不大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就算是龍彥也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:21.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:22.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,撫子快加速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:23.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶 過來這邊這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:45.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不好好洗洗的話 波奇又會去嗅屁屁的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,閉嘴 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,零分玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,平穩 靜謐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,真想一直留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.56,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留 停還是不停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.48,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,總之還是繼續開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們慢慢地走就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留 高爾夫球好多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:41.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,真的 好多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:42.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,慘了×N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}玲實 很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.31,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,快點說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我剛剛想到了很不妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,比如武藏橫手站的山羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,高麗站植物根莖一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.31,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這裡所在的球會不會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,以前 全都住在車站周邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.00,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:12.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這人都是球啊 快快快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:13.01,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊啊 夠了 討厭討厭討厭討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼是恐怖的車站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.25,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留 快點出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,剛剛說過的 那個 是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,午餐包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是鐵道轉折器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,它會從這裡一直通往另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們把裝載的行李換到後面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:31.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的是 竟是些可怕的車站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,情況越來越糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:36.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的是 不如像吾野一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:38.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是個人就可以和他們交談就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你又是想拿我取笑了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,說起來能夠說話的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:48.93,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就可以說謊 也可以說我不喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,也可以吵架什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:54.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要是能夠減少一粒紛爭的種子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:57.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不說話或許也不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:13:00.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,然後 就坐在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,黑暗 安靜的 地面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.10,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼要藏起屁屁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:08.79,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我沒有藏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:12.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:13.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:14.91,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:16.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:18.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:18.61,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:19.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不能不看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.14,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.49,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶 這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.71,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:30.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什麼時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.78,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我什麼狀況都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶她長蘑菇了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:35.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.86,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這邊我沒有問題 那邊就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.56,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要 不要拔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,明明都和平共處那麼久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.41,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這樣子的話一兩年後你就會死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.07,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.73,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,悲觀主義也挺酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我對這個完全搞不懂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:51.10,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,才不願意生活在焦慮的水深火熱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶 你以前就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:55.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,憤世嫉俗 喋喋不休 五十步笑百步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,零分玲實靈長類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你自己有了什麼事情 從來都不告訴別人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,遇到那麼多麻煩 都勉強自己堅強起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}蘑菇 蘑菇 蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:07.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,實際上超級膽小 超級愛哭鬼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.13,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吶 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.28,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:31.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實 靜留 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.75,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,大家都好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,小晶可是一直都精神飽滿的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.95,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,生氣勃勃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.39,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,總感覺很 奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.91,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.52,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,小晶才不奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.40,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,生氣氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們那時候不是直接恢復了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:52.07,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你個玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.10,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這麼大聲說話的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:54.61,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,無依無靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:58.53,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,難道是因為蘑菇長得太大了導致的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:14:59.98,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,時間過得挺久的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:00.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,也就是說有些沒用的也被一起拔了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,總之先坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,來吧小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:10.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嘿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.93,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,總感覺不能隨意動彈吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.28,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這個是 我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感覺好舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}感覺好可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是靈魂 是靈魂被拔了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.89,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶令人討厭 非主流的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.16,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.73,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,根本找不到醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:37.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,果然天鵝仙人的地圖是亂畫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,回吾野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,現在水應該退卻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:41.58,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,回去了也沒有人能治好她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.30,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且鐵軌也是彎曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那 要是小晶她就這樣死掉了怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要 這種事情不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冷靜下來 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:50.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.90,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,必須要治好她的玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.47,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,畢竟 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:16:00.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,從今天開始你的名字就叫「安東尼」啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,拜託了善治郎先生 請告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:09.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,以後無論什麼事情 咱再也不會說你的壞話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.76,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:13.45,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,那傢伙會直接對大腦產生影響
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.30,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.74,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,現在 還有反應的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然嘴臭 但確實醫術高明的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,以前一起合作過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:27.27,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小學的時候 尿褲子了 還把責任推到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:33.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,考試作弊 豎琴 流口水事件 全部都扯上了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,現在 在稻荷山公園 吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,糟老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稻荷山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是指稻荷山公園嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 我想是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:47.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 咖哩味便便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.58,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不要說什麼便便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:51.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個時候小晶她說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:56.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,和代大姐說 在稻荷山公園有個醫術高超的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:56.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,水豚的和代大姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:58.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,她說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,只是不知道對方是否人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:05.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,再者說稻荷山公園 現在到底是什麼樣子的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.02,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不用慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:07.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:13.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,穩紮穩打 但要快速到達那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留 怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:32.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個 沒有人在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 廁所能用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,還有自來水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我就去個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.22,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.21,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:41.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我會看著小晶的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,終於能說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.30,ZH-Main-Down,Jizo,0,0,0,,那是當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.44,ZH-Main-Down,Jizo,0,0,0,,別小看地藏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,稻荷山公園是個什麼地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.78,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有人類的醫生在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.31,ZH-Main-Down,Jizo,0,0,0,,別問我這些嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.03,ZH-Main-Down,Jizo,0,0,0,,我們動不了又到不了那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.79,ZH-Main-Down,Jizo,0,0,0,,但一旦習慣不動如山就能輕鬆很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:18:00.34,ZH-Main-Down,Jizo,0,0,0,,難得留下來供奉給我的食物卻吃不了雖有些生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.40,ZH-Main-Down,Jizo,0,0,0,,但稻荷山公園距離這就兩站遠對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:04.77,ZH-Main-Down,Jizo,0,0,0,,我就知道這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.00,ZH-Main-Down,Jizo,0,0,0,,不知道有沒有醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.06,ZH-Main-Down,Jizo,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:26.78,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,內臟 內臟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,內臟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:42.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那麼就拜託你了撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,照顧好小晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:43.84,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.72,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留 玲實就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯 為什麼要我拜託給你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:51.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,醫者不自醫 渡人不渡己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 誰 我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,意義不明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,敲這不什麼都沒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:05.12,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,別說醫生了 連人影都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯 感覺什麼響了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:12.83,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯 感覺有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,像是牆壁一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 不會吧 我看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不愧是視力25的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:23.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是啦 是2.5
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,, 又響了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:26.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留 到了 是城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感覺這邊好像沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.73,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 剛剛你聽到了奇怪的聲音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,聽到了聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那種聲音肯定是人類所發出的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們去轉一圈看看發生了什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}不行 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.78,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,早點找到醫生 把小晶她帶過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不如說好小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 這是哪裡 格列佛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.71,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感覺好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,總感覺像是世界廣場一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:20:00.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 我感覺那裡會比這還小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:02.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然沒有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:03.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,沒有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:08.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好厲害 好久沒見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.52,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.75,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,{\an8}這什麼這什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:21.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好痛 但是沒什麼效果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:25.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 確實 這是什麼鬼啊敲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:28.48,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,好痛×N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.80,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,像是娃娃一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:42.03,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,好痛×N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:45.18,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這東西多大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:48.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個就是說 我們沒有惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:55.44,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,好痛×N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:08.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:11.25,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶 等會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈 終於追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:16.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:20.75,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,明天日語考試 我完全不知道該如何複習
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,告訴我如何得分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.75,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要這樣做的話 你就不是零分倒數了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:27.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我想進步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:31.72,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,教科書或者詞典
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,想要記下來的部分撕下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,整合之後壓成餅乾食用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:37.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 好厲害 不愧是小晶
